 🌐 Terraform AWS Static Website with HTTPS (S3 + CloudFront)

This project uses [Terraform](https://www.terraform.io/) to deploy a static website to AWS S3 and deliver it securely over HTTPS using CloudFront.

---

## 📦 What This Project Does

- Creates an S3 bucket to host a static website
- Uploads your `index.html` file
- Restricts public access to the bucket
- Configures a CloudFront distribution for global delivery
- Enables HTTPS via CloudFront's default certificate

---

## 🛠 Prerequisites

- ✅ [Terraform Installed](https://developer.hashicorp.com/terraform/downloads)
- ✅ AWS Account
- ✅ AWS CLI configured **or** export credentials:
  ```bash
  export AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID="your-access-key"
  export AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY="your-secret-key"
